        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">7</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、不与甲方人员就汽车经销、服务等相关事项私下进行交涉或交易，以达成某种默契。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Do not negotiate or do business or reach secret agreement with personnel of Party A regarding to auto sales and service in privacy. </span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">8</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、不接受甲方人员及其“特定关系人”从事与甲方汽车经销业务相关的经济活动。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Do not allow personnel or “specific relevant party” of Party A to participate in auto sales related activities of Party A.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">9</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、不接受甲方人员及其“特定关系人”在乙方投资入股。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Do not allow personnel or “specific relevant party” of Party A to invest or take share in business of Party B.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">10</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、不以任何理由为甲方人员及其“特定关系人”提供、给付不正当利益或达成不正当利益的分成。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Don’t provide or offer illegitimate profits or reach agreement about illegal profit dividend for Party A in person and the specific relevant party. </span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">11</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、不进行任何会干扰甲方行使或履行相关合同规定的权利或义务的活动，包括但不限于任何涉及不正当商业利益或非法的行为。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Don’t take any action that may disturb Party A to exercise or fulfill the rights or obligation described in the related contract, including but not limited to the acts that are illegal or involved in illegitimate business profits. </span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">12</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、不利用任何社会关系影响、干扰甲方在整车销售和售后服务方面的流程和业务活动。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Don’t affect or disturb vehicle sales or after sales service related process or business activities of Party A by utilizing all kinds of social relationship.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">13</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、乙方及乙方人员从未有诈骗、腐败或不道德行为，从未被列入政府限制对象的名单中。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Neither Party B nor any of its personnel should have fraud, corruption, or immoral behavior record or listed in any government restricted parties list.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">14</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、乙方保证，在履行与甲方的相关合同</span><span style="font-size:13px">/</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">协议时，乙方及乙方人员从未也不会直接或间接的向政府官员提供、承诺提供或提议提供任何现金或其他有价之物，以期为甲方获取或保留业务或获得不正当优势。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Party B hereby guarantees to Party A that during the contract and agreement performance, neither Party B nor its personnel should directly or indirectly provide or promise to provide, suggest offer cash or any other items of values so as to secure or retain business or obtain any improper advantage for party A.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">15</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、乙方同意提交的所有发票、报告、声明、商簿或记录在各个方面都真实准确，并且全面准确地描述所提供的服务、货物内容以及费用和<span>/</span>或付款的性质和对象。乙方同意根据甲方的要求提供其准确编制商簿和记录所需的所有重要信息。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Party B agrees that all invoices, reports, declaration, books or records are in truth and accuracy with the nature and objectives of service, goods content, expense and/or payment in overall precise description. Party B agrees to provide all the important information that the books and records precise compiling necessity based on Party A request.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">16</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、乙方同意及时向甲方提供甲方认为核实乙方遵守其合同义务所需的商簿和记录，并且按照甲方不时提出的合理要求，确认其对于法律、法规的遵守。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Party B agrees to provide Party A with prompt access to its books and records as Party A’s consideration of the necessity of confirming Party B’s compliance with its obligations and confirm its compliance with laws and regulations as may from time to time reasonably request.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">17、未取得甲方书面批准之前，乙方不会就其在与甲方的相关合同<span>/</span>协议项下义务的履行直接或间接地向任何个人或公司支付佣金、中间人费用或推荐费用。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Party B will not pay or tender, directly or indirectly, any commission or intermediaries or referral fees to any person or firm in connection with carrying out the responsibilities described in this Agreement and/or other transactions with Party A (if any) without the prior written approval of Party A.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px;font-family:黑体">五、违约责任</span><a name="OLE_LINK8"></a><a name="OLE_LINK7"></a><span style="font-size: 13px;">Responsibility for Breach of Contract</span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">1</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、乙方人员违反本协议的，甲方有权选择立即中止、终止或解除与乙方的销售</span><span style="font-size:13px">/</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">服务合同或正在进行的任何交易关系，由此造成的不利后果及甲方和甲方人员的损失由乙方自行承担。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Party A is entitled to suspend, terminate or relieve the engineering construction or purchase contract or any ongoing transaction relationship with Party B if Party B violates the agreement and Party B shall bear all the unfavorable consequence and the loss of party A and party A&#39;s personnel thereby.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">2</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、乙方人员违反本协议的，一经查实，乙方须依法依纪严肃处理，追究有关人员的责任，触犯法律的移交司法机关处理。由此造成甲方的损失由乙方承担。</span>
        </p>
        <p style="line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">Party B shall conduct the case seriously, investigate the responsibility if personnel of Party B violate the agreement and may hand over related personnel to judicial authority if personnel violate the law and shall bear all the loss of Party A thereby.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">3</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、甲方人员如有违反本协议条款或国家法律法规的行为，乙方应向甲方纪检监察部门如实举报，甲方应对乙方举报人、举报内容和举报行为进行保密，不得对乙方进行打击报复。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Party B is entitled to report the truth to the discipline inspection and supervision department if Party A violates the agreement. Party A shall keep confidentiality for reporter, report content and report behavior of Party B. Attack or revenge to Party B is forbidden.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px;font-family:黑体">六、其它约定</span><span style="font-size: 13px">Other agreement </span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">1</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、因本协议产生的或与本协议有关的一切争议，双方应协商解决，协商不成，任何一方均有权向甲方所在地人民法院提起诉讼。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Any argument that generates from or is related to the agreement shall be and settled by bilateral negotiation. Either party is entitled to initiate legal proceedings to local People’s Court of Party B if negotiation fails.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px">2</span><span style="font-size:13px;font-family:宋体">、甲乙双方同意本协议适用中华人民共和国法律。</span><span style="font-size:13px">Both parties agree that the agreement applies to the laws of the People’s Republic of China.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="text-indent:27px;line-height:33px">
            <br/>
        </p>
        <p style="line-height:33px">
            <span style="font-size:13px;font-family:黑体">七、本协议为双方签署的汽车产品供销合同、维修服务合同的附件，与汽车产品供销合同、维修服务合同具有同等法律效力。本协议一式三份，甲方执二份、乙方执一份，本协议自双方签字盖章之日起生效。</span><span style="font-size:13px">This&nbsp;agreement will be the annex of vehicle supply and marketing contract and maintenance service&nbsp;<a><span style="color:windowtext;text-underline:none">contract</span></a> signed by both parties and have the&nbsp;equal legal&nbsp;effect. This agreement is in triplicate. Party A may keep two copies, party B may keep one copy. The&nbsp;agreement&nbsp;takes&nbsp;effect as of the date of signature and seal by both parties.</span>
        </p>
        <p style="line-height:33px">
            <br/>
        </p>
